Process for upgrading between versions of the PLM

- Disable plm_supervisor.pl cron jobs
- Kill any running plm_supervisor.pl processes
- Update the PLM install on each of the plm_supervisor.pl machines
- If SQL changes will break the website, shut down the website
- Run the SQL upgrade script against the Database
- Update the PLM install on the ASP server
- Update the PLM install on the Web server (sometimes the same as the ASP server)
- Test web interface
- Test execution of plm_supervisor.pl script
- Enable the plm_supervisor.pl CRON jobs
